block.air_lock_frame.description: Air Lock Frames, when arranged in a portal-like formation, with a single block replaced with a controller, will function as a working air lock. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.aluminum_wire.alu_wire.description: Le câble en aluminum est utilisé pour connecter des sources d'énergies à des machines qui en ont besoin.
block.aluminum_wire.alu_wire_heavy.descr: Le câble en aluminum lourd est utilisé pour connecter des sources d'énergies à des machines qui en ont besoin. Transfers à plus haut débit que son prédécesseur.
block.arclamp.description: Les lampes ARC sont utilisées pour éclairer fortement une large zone, provocant la fuite de la plupart des mobs.
block.buggy_pad.description: Fueling Pads will allow a buggy on the pad to be refueled by an attached Fuel Loaders if set up in a 3x3 square.  Cannot be used to launch rockets! ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.cargo_loader.description: Cargo Loaders will pass blocks and items onto Rockets and other vehicles with cargo space. Must be attached to Landing/Fueling pad. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.cargo_unloader.description: Cargo Unloaders will extract blocks and items from Rockets and other vehicles with cargo space. Must be attached to Landing/Fueling pad. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.cheese.description: Cheese Blocks are created from the cheeses of the Moon, place-able and edible. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.circuit_fabricator.description: Circuit Fabricator will process basic materials into silicon wafers, used for advanced machines. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.coal_generator.description: Coal Generator will simply burn coal for energy collection. The simplest but least efficient energy collection method. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.collector.description: Le collecteur d'oxygène stockera l'oxygène rassemblé des feuilles dans les environs.
block.compressor.description: Compressor will process ingots into their compressed equivalents. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.compressor_electric.description: Electric Compressor will process ingots into their compressed equivalents. Compresses two at a time, making it more effective than it's predecessor. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.dishbase.description: The Communications Dish can track the position of space stations and receive communications from your remote space bases. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.distributor.description: Le distributeur d'oxygène émettra une bulle d'oxygène à l'extérieur du bloc de centre en utilisant le réservoir interne. Ceci permet une respiration saine à l'intérieur de la bulle.
block.electric_furnace_tier1.description: Electric Furnace is used as a faster alternative to traditional coal furnaces. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.electric_furnace_tier2.description: Arc Furnace is used as a faster alternative to both traditional coal and electric furnaces. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.enclosed.description: Sealable blocks should be used where air cannot pass, such as space base walls. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.enclosed.glass_fibre_cable: Câble hermétique en fibres de verre
block.enclosed.lv_cable: Câble hermétique à courant ultra faible
block.enclosed.pipe_items_cobblestone: Tuyau hermétique de tranport en pierre
block.enclosed.pipe_items_stone: Tuyau hermétique de tranport en roche
block.energy_storage_module_tier1.descri: Energy Storage Module is used to store large amounts of energy for later use. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.energy_storage_module_tier2.descri: Energy Storage Cluster is used to store large amounts of energy for later use. Stores and outputs more energy than it's predecessor. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.fallen_meteor.description: Fallen Meteors can be found in many planets/moons which have little or no atmosphere. Will drop Meteoric Iron when broken. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.fuel_loader.description: Après avoir été connecté à la rampe de lancement, le chargeur de carburant autorisera le carburant à passer dans les fusées ou les autre véhicules connectés.
block.glowstone_torch.description: Glowstone Torches are best used to light areas when there is no oxygen for wood torches to burn. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.landing_pad.description: La rampe de lancement autorisera le placement de fusées si elle est configuré en carré de 3x3. Chargeur de carburant, chargeur de cargo et controleurs de lancement peuvent lui être attaché.
block.moon_stairs_brick: Escaliers en briques de donjon lunaire
block.oxygen_compressor.description: Le compresseur d'oxygène chargera l'oxygène du stockage interne dans un réservoir d'oxygène.
block.oxygen_decompressor.description: Le décompresseur d'oxygène déchargera l'oxygène dans le stockage interne d'un réservoir d'oxygène.
block.oxygen_detector.description: Le détecteur d'oxygène émettra un signal redstone quand il sera entouré d'oxygène.
block.oxygen_pipe.description: Le tuyau d'oxygène transfèrera l'oxygene du réservoir à gaz interne d'une machine vers une autre.
block.oxygen_storage_module.description: Oxygen Storage Module is used to store large amounts of oxygen for later use. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.parachest.description: Parachests will fall from the sky after landing on certain planets/moons, such as Earth. Contains rocket, fuel, and cargo from previous launch. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.refinery.description: La rafinerie prendra en entrée du pétrole et de l'énergie et en sortie du carburant utilisé par les fusée et les véhicules.
block.rocket_workbench.description: The NASA Workbench is used to create many advanced parts and vehicles. New schematics can be added as they are found. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.sealer.description: Le scellant d'oxygène vérifiera le confinement de l'espace. Si un est trouvé, la zone sera rempli d'air respirable.
block.slab_gc_half.moon_bricks_slab: Dalle en briques de donjon lunaire
block.solar_adv.description: Advanced Solar Panels will collect energy from the sun, storing it for further use. Automatically adjusts panel angle for optimal energy collection. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.solar_basic.description: Basic Solar Panels will collect energy from the sun, storing it for further use. Collects most energy at mid-day (non-adjustable). ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.spin_thruster.description: Spin Thrusters are used to make space stations rotate. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.telemetry.description: This gathers useful data from linked rockets, players and mobs. Best placed near to a Display Screen. Use a Frequency Module to establish data links. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.treasure_chest.description: Tier 1 Treasure Chests will generate in Moon Dungeons. They are unlockable after defeating the final boss. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.view_screen.description: Display screens add that final touch to your space base. Right-click changes the information shown. ##NEEDS TRANSLATE##
block.wall_gc.moon_bricks: Mur en briques de donjon lunaire
